_sText:
I've been working on this map off and on for a very long time.  It's in it's beta form and I don't plan on making a final.  Find any leaks, you can mention them, but I most likely won't fix them because I don't care for this map too much.  I paked it using pakrat so all needed files are in the bsp including the nav.

have fun, enjoy it, if you add it to a server TELL ME!!

Thanks Chizbone for making a new better nav!
